{"tid":894761,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"補完牙 隻牙仲痛過未補","createTime":"2018-11-08T15:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T07:59:35.000Z","uid":1022,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b1afb21b3a8b3e668fc88635df509f94a54e5fc4","tid":894761,"uid":1022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:33:28.000Z","msg":"上個月去補牙，佢話我牙罅蛀左<br />\n<br />\n補完兩日我食雪凍左既提子，一咬落去補果個位好似被野電咁 勁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我返去比佢檢查<br />\n佢堅持d補料無甩無問題<br />\n塞左兩枝舒適達比我就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家連飲常溫水滲落隻牙度都痛，唔洗講話甜野凍野<br />\n我應該搵過第個牙醫睇，定搵幫我補呢條友尋仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb260bab22a3e9dfb757c7a4c68e5cb4a8962564","tid":894761,"uid":196791,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:38:34.000Z","msg":"搵其他牙醫睇啦<br />\n我睇開嗰個幾好，之前試過喺佢度一次過補三隻，補完之後完全唔痛，keep到而加都冇事<br />\n利申：廢事俾人話打手，想知留tg"},{"pid":"1bce18b5561a973edcfa9d2a0afa6a822bc9bb78","tid":894761,"uid":123304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cb260bab22a3e9dfb757c7a4c68e5cb4a8962564","tid":894761,"uid":196791,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:38:34.000Z","msg":"搵其他牙醫睇啦<br />\n我睇開嗰個幾好，之前試過喺佢度一次過補三隻，補完之後完全唔痛，keep到而加都冇事<br />\n利申：廢事俾人話打手，想知留tg"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:39:20.000Z","msg":"打非中?"},{"pid":"0f4aae99b7846ad3accde6aee5c60b257afe061a","tid":894761,"uid":1022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bce18b5561a973edcfa9d2a0afa6a822bc9bb78","tid":894761,"uid":123304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cb260bab22a3e9dfb757c7a4c68e5cb4a8962564","tid":894761,"uid":196791,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:38:34.000Z","msg":"搵其他牙醫睇啦<br />\n我睇開嗰個幾好，之前試過喺佢度一次過補三隻，補完之後完全唔痛，keep到而加都冇事<br />\n利申：廢事俾人話打手，想知留tg"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:39:2